## Attribution

This package (graphify_pkg) is a bootstrap kit for Graphify
(https://github.com/safishamsi/graphify), which is independently released under
the MIT License (Copyright (c) 2026 Safi Shamsi).

This package does NOT redistribute Graphify's source code. It provides
documentation, templates, and configuration helpers (CLAUDE.md section,
.claude/settings.json PreToolUse hook, .graphifyignore patterns, and a
Claude Code bootstrap skill) for using Graphify in code workspaces.

The CLAUDE.md graphify section template (templates/claude-md-section.template.md)
and PreToolUse hook (templates/claude-settings-hook.json) are content produced
by `graphify claude install` and are reproduced here under Graphify's MIT
License for offline reference and manual integration.

For Graphify itself (CLI, library, and skill), refer to the upstream project:
https://github.com/safishamsi/graphify
